derivation: or כִּנֶּרֶתlemma כִּנֶרֶת missing dagesh, corrected to כִּנֶּרֶת; respectively plural and singular feminine from the same as H3658 (כִּנּוֹר); perhaps harp-shaped;
outline:
Chinneroth or Cinneroth or Chinnereth = "harps"
  1. the early name of the Sea of Galilee
  2. a town and district in Naphtali near the Sea of Galilee
strongs_def: Kinneroth or Kinnereth, a place in Palestine
